thread.title: Marco Parenti
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Marco Parenti

author: Marco Parenti
title: Marco Parenti
text:
Everything ok except the staff who gives us the car in Auckland.
She didn't give us informations on the car and was not very helpful.
At the opposite each time we phoned during our travel we had very kind persons and good informations.
In Christchurch staff were very nice and kind
